API For Register User:-

Method:-
POST

1.URL:-
localhost:8080/register

ReqBody:-



{
	            "firstName":"Ashwini",
	            "employeeCode":"1",
                "lastName":"More",
                "password":"ashwini123",
                "email":"ashwini10@gmail.com",
                "organizationName":"quest"
}


Note:-

one user register only once (Unique employee code)

==================================================================

API For login User:-
Method:-
POST

2.URL:-
localhost:8080/login

ReqBody:-{
	
	          
              "password":"ashwini123",
                "email":"ashwini1@gmail.com"
	       
}

Note:-

only Register user able to login

=============================================================

API For get user data:-
Method:-
POST

URL:-
localhost:8080/employee/get

Headers:-

Authorization:-Token(will getting from login api)

ReqBody:-


   {
	
"search":"di",
"page":1,
"limit":2
}


